19 23-63-2105. State audit automated utilization management system.
20 (a) The Insurance Commissioner may audit at any time a healthcare
21 insurer's automated utilization management system.
22 (b) The commissioner may contract with a third-party entity to perform
23 an audit under subsection (a) of this section.
